-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
			Fighter Commands
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Command                                Description
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
fhelp <command>                        Will tell you more about the command.
frestore tabard                        Fixes your guild object.
fwho                                   Version of "who" that only shows your 
                                       guild members.
declare <text>                         Declares a motto visible on "fwho".
fchat                                  Version of tell that lets you talk to
                                       all your guild members. 
efchat                                 Guild channel emote.
fhist                                  This shows a history of all communi-
                                       cations on the Fighter channel.
fs/fskills                             A current list of skills.
fstats                                 As a fighter, stats are kept on your
                                       overall career, and over just your
                                       login.
fassist                                This allows you to call for help to      
                                       your fighter brethren while fighting a
                                       tough opponent.
flost                                  This allows you to call for help to
                                       your fighter brethren when you are
                                       lost.

fcrush <item>                          This is a fun alternative to the "junk"
                                       command which allows you to crush a
                                       given item in your hands.
fgrunt <text>                          This command allows you to grunt the
                                       given text out in a series of grunts
                                       that only a fellow fighter, or your
                                       squire, could possibly understand.
fmess <login|logout> <message>         This command allows you to customize the
                                       message used when you log in and out of
                                       Darkwind.
ftimers                                This command shows you when you can use
                                       abilities that use a specific timer.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
